headline: There's Still Time to Raise a Glass for Pediatric Cancer Research
summary: For the 14th consecutive year, Florida's largest family-owned wine and spirits retailer, ABC Fine Wine & Spirits (ABC) ,has partnered with the National Pediatric Cancer Foundation (NPCF), and Constellation Brands to raise funds for lifesaving childhood cancer research.
